# Python File Handling & Exception Handling Assignment

## 📌 Description
This assignment demonstrates:
- File reading & writing.
- Error handling for missing or unreadable files.

## 🖋️ Task 1: File Read & Write
- Reads text from `input.txt`.
- Converts content to uppercase.
- Writes the modified text into `output.txt`.

Run with:
```bash
python file_read_write.py
